This project is an SDLC skill kit that extends the Superpowers plugin for
Claude Code (https://github.com/obra/superpowers) by Jesse Vincent (obra).

The kit's skills invoke Superpowers skills (e.g. superpowers:brainstorming,
superpowers:writing-plans) rather than copying their text. Superpowers is an
independent project under its own license; this project neither vendors nor
modifies it. Install Superpowers separately (see README).
